    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Overview:</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the year 2000, explorers discovered a hidden Hindu civilization submerged under the Indian Ocean. They found ancient statues of Brahma, Vishnu, and Mahesh emitting a mysterious, dark energy. The site was filled with only corpses and abandoned Hindu statues remaining. Secretly, Indian and global scientists began experimenting with the statues, trying to harness their power. However, one experiment went terribly wrong, causing a massive explosion that created a black hole. This black hole led to a collision between different dimensions and magical worlds in the multiverse. As a result, anomalies started occurring all around the world. To protect the world and hide the truth, a secret society was formed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026030/extras/424e9ace7430ceac28218f8763433139.poster.avif?t=1730979263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026030/extras/424e9ace7430ceac28218f8763433139.webm?t=1730979263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Key Features:</i></strong>  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action Pack :</strong> Engage in thrilling, myth-inspired combat with diverse weapons and destructible environments that enhance strategic play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026030/extras/d06d8b7a57b37563c3c478719b625253.poster.avif?t=1730979263\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st